Package ktt.lib.httpserver.handler

Class FilePreHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • ktt.lib.httpserver.RequestHandler
      • ktt.lib.httpserver.handler.FilePreHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Authenticator
    public class FilePreHandler
extends RequestHandler
    A Request Handler that returns a file and preloaded bytes.
    Methods that use the FileBytesAdapter will preload bytes using FileBytesAdapter.getBytes(File).
    Methods that use the FileNameAdapter will name the files using FileNameAdapter.getName(File). This will only name files, not the directories themselves.
